Memory Usage Alert (Used %)
(1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100
Format: Time series

Type: Range

Step: 15s
Expression C (Threshold):

Input: A

Condition: IS ABOVE 85

